# Editor
.vscode/
.idea/

# Your personal model data stays on your machine, never in git.
# The real hypotheses, sessions, and experiments you generate are excluded from
# version control by default — only the worked example and the folder READMEs
# are tracked. (Want to keep your own private history in a *private* repo
# instead? Delete the matching lines below.)
cognitive-model/hypotheses/*
!cognitive-model/hypotheses/H000-example-notification-checking.md
cognitive-model/sessions/*
!cognitive-model/sessions/README.md
cognitive-model/experiments/*
!cognitive-model/experiments/README.md
